               <code code="34069-5" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="HOW SUPPLIED SECTION"/>
               <title>HOW SUPPLIED</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Clindamycin Phosphate Topical Solution, USP 1% containing clindamycin phosphate equivalent to 10 mg clindamycin per milliliter is available in the following sizes: 
       
 
  <br/>30 mL applicator bottles – NDC 0472-0987-91 
       
 
  <br/>60 mL applicator bottles – NDC 0472-0987-92 
      

 </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">Store at 20°-25°C (68°-77°F) [See USP Controlled Room Temperature].
        
  
   <br/>Protect from freezing.
       
 
  </content>
                  </paragraph>
